steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"9u7ok","text":"Dilute the peptide sample with solvent A (2% ACN, 0.1% FA) to the desired concentration. Transfer the samples to an autosampler vial and add iRT peptides to the sample according to the manufacturer’s instructions.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"bb0ig","text":"Inject the sample onto a Dionex UltiMate 3000 liquid chromatographic system coupled to an Orbitrap Eclipse Tribrid mass spectrometer and load the peptides on a C18 trap column over 10 min at 5 µL/min with 100% solvent A.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"sub","offset":161,"length":2}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4oufp","text":"Elute the peptides with a C18 analytical column heated at 35°C and at a flow rate of 300 nL/min over 215 min using the following gradient of solvent B:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"sub","offset":27,"length":2}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ci3u8","text":"Acquire the data in data-independent acquisition (DIA) mode using the settings described in Table 1. One cycle consists of one full MS scan collected in the Orbitrap analyzer followed by DIA-MS/MS scans collected in the Orbitrap analyzer based on an isolation scheme of 26 variable windows covering the 350 - 1,650 m/z range with an overlap of 1 m/z (Table 2).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":92,"length":7},{"style":"bold","offset":351,"length":7}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9oe4j","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"apo00","text":"      ","type":"align-center","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":1,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"9nvsk","text":"\n\n","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dj9cv","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ekb61","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a0i1d","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"l3mp","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6bhlj","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"image","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"D7B498406F9511EE81670A58A9FEAC02","height":769.0945454545454,"is_video":false,"legend":"{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"bpqf9\",\"text\":\"Table 1.
